OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782733687
OL,3,CTwo boys pulled from debris days after
OL,4,CVenezuela quakes as rescue window
OL,5,Cnarrows
OL,7,FTwo 11-year-old boys have been pulled
OL,8,Falive from the rubble days after two
OL,9,Fpowerful earthquakes struck Venezuela,
OL,10,Fas fears grow that the death toll will
OL,11,Fcontinue to rise.
OL,13,FThe quakes - which hit within seconds
OL,14,Fof each other on Wednesday and
OL,15,Fmeasured magnitudes of 7.2 and 7.5 -
OL,16,Fhave killed at least 1,430 people,
OL,17,Fwith tens of thousands still believed
OL,18,Fto be missing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
