OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782733687
OL,3,CTwo boys pulled from debris days after
OL,4,CVenezuela quakes as rescue window
OL,5,Cnarrows
OL,7,FAid agencies say that after an
OL,8,Fearthquake, the first 72 hours are
OL,9,Fcritical to saving lives, although
OL,10,Fthis window can be longer if those
OL,11,Ftrapped have access to food and water.
OL,13,FVideo footage shows the moment one
OL,14,Fboy, Moises, was pulled from the
OL,15,Frubble by rescuers on Saturday to loud
OL,16,Fapplause.
OL,18,FThe moment Moises, 11, was pulled from
OL,19,Fthe debris on Saturday
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782733687
OL,3,CTwo boys pulled from debris days after
OL,4,CVenezuela quakes as rescue window
OL,5,Cnarrows
OL,7,FColumbia's National Unit for Disaster
OL,8,FRisk Management (UNGRD), which shared
OL,9,Fthe footage, said he was buried under
OL,10,Fabout three metres of debris in La
OL,11,FGuaira, one of the hardest-hit states.
OL,13,F"After six hours of high-precision
OL,14,Fwork, our rescuers managed to reach
OL,15,Fthe boy who was at a depth of 3 meters
OL,16,Fand extract him safely," they wrote on
OL,17,FX.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782733687
OL,3,CTwo boys pulled from debris days after
OL,4,CVenezuela quakes as rescue window
OL,5,Cnarrows
OL,7,FVenezuela's Acting President, Delcy
OL,8,FRodriguez, later posted a video on X,
OL,9,Fappearing to show the rescue of a
OL,10,Fsecond 11-year-old boy, this time in
OL,11,Fthe town of Caraballeda.
OL,13,FShe wrote: "In these hours, every life
OL,14,Fis hope for Venezuela."
OL,16,FElsewhere, another story of recovery
OL,17,Fhas been shared by teams on the
OL,18,Fground, with American rescuers pulling
OL,19,Fa baby from the rubble of a collapsed
OL,20,Fbuilding on Saturday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
