FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782733687
OL,3,CTwo boys pulled from debris days after
OL,4,CVenezuela quakes as rescue window
OL,5,Cnarrows
OL,7,FThe Virginia Task Force 1 Urban Search
OL,8,Fand Rescue shared the footage online,
OL,9,Fas did the US State Department.
OL,11,FIt said the infant was nine months
OL,12,Fold, and both the infant and its
OL,13,Fmother were rescued from a collapsed
OL,14,Fstructure.
OL,16,F"Both were found alive with only minor
OL,17,Finjuries, brought to safety to the
OL,18,Fcheers of neighbors (sic)."
OL,20,F"Every life saved is a victory," the
OL,21,FUS State Department added.
