OL,3,CTwo boys pulled from debris days after
OL,4,CVenezuela quakes as rescue window
OL,5,Cnarrows
OL,7,FIn La Guaira, residents searching for
OL,8,Floved ones used shovels, heavy
OL,9,Fmachinery, ropes and even their bare
OL,10,Fhands to comb through mounds of
OL,11,Fcollapsed concrete. They were joined
OL,12,Fby a growing number of international
OL,13,Fteams picking their way through the
OL,14,Frubble, offering a fragile glimmer of
OL,15,Fhope to waiting families.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
