OL,3,CTwo boys pulled from debris days after
OL,4,CVenezuela quakes as rescue window
OL,5,Cnarrows
OL,7,FMeanwhile, Rodriguez told state
OL,8,Ftelevision that more than 14,000
OL,9,Fmilitary and police personnel had been
OL,10,Fdeployed to the area, where access is
OL,11,Fnow restricted, and special permits
OL,12,Fare required to enter.
