OL,7,FAny Britons requiring assistance are
OL,8,Fadvised to follow the advice of local
OL,9,Fauthorities and contact +58 (0) 212
OL,10,F263 8411 from Venezuela and 0207 008
OL,11,F5000 from the UK if they require
OL,12,Furgent assistance.
